        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
            <div class="text-4xl text-soft-sage mb-4 opacity-50">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-6xl">format_quote</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic leading-snug">"Choosing software shouldn't feel like a chore. It should feel like the first step to your new lifestyle."</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-expert-navy/70 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                When I started my first salon, I spent months wrestling with spreadsheets. It wasn't until I found a tool that 'clicked' that I actually started to grow. At Salongroei, we look beyond the feature listsâ€”we look at the *feeling* and the flow. We want you to love your tools as much as your clients love their results.
            </p>
            <div class="w-32 h-[2px] bg-primary mb-6"></div>
            <button class="bg-primary/20 text-primary px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold text-sm hover:bg-primary transition-all hover:text-white">
                Read My Story
